---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ICN Roadmap" description="The development roadmap for the InterCooperative Network">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="bg-accent-primary/20 text-accent-primary border border-accent-primary/30 text-sm font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4 inline-block">
          ROADMAP
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">ICN Development Roadmap</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-light-slate max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          20 development phases complete with 1,134+ passing tests.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <!-- Status Banner -->
        <div class="bg-accent-primary/10 p-6 rounded-lg border border-accent-primary/30 mb-8">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-accent-primary">Current Status: In Development</h3>
              <p class="text-light-slate mt-1">Core infrastructure complete. Continuing development.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-4 text-center">
              <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-primary">20</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-gray">Phases</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-primary">1,134+</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-gray">Tests</div>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-primary">16</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-gray">Crates</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Core Substrate (Phases 0-7) -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-accent-primary/20">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-primary mb-3">Core Substrate (Phases 0-7) âœ…</h3>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-4">
            Foundation infrastructure with identity, trust, networking, ledger, contracts, gossip, and hardening.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-1 text-sm">
              <li>â€¢ DIDs with Ed25519 cryptography</li>
              <li>â€¢ Web-of-participation trust graph</li>
              <li>â€¢ QUIC/TLS secure networking</li>
              <li>â€¢ mDNS peer discovery</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-1 text-sm">
              <li>â€¢ Mutual credit ledger (Merkle-DAG)</li>
              <li>â€¢ Cooperative Contract Language (CCL)</li>
              <li>â€¢ Gossip protocol with trust gating</li>
              <li>â€¢ Rate limiting & security hardening</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Advanced Features (Phases 8-14) -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-accent-primary/20">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-primary mb-3">Advanced Features (Phases 8-14) âœ…</h3>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-4">
            Multi-device identity, economic safety, governance v1, REST gateway, distributed compute, and storage.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-1 text-sm">
              <li>â€¢ Multi-device identity (DID Document v2)</li>
              <li>â€¢ Dynamic credit limits</li>
              <li>â€¢ Dispute resolution mechanisms</li>
              <li>â€¢ Domain-based governance proposals</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-1 text-sm">
              <li>â€¢ REST API gateway (60+ endpoints)</li>
              <li>â€¢ Distributed compute layer</li>
              <li>â€¢ Storage replication</li>
              <li>â€¢ Federation coordination</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Production Ready (Phases 15-20) -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-accent-primary/20">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-primary mb-3">Production Ready (Phases 15-20) âœ…</h3>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-4">
            Byzantine detection, privacy enhancements, observability, and operational hardening.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-1 text-sm">
              <li>â€¢ Byzantine node detection</li>
              <li>â€¢ Privacy enhancements</li>
              <li>â€¢ Prometheus metrics integration</li>
              <li>â€¢ Real-time monitoring dashboards</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-1 text-sm">
              <li>â€¢ Encrypted backup/restore</li>
              <li>â€¢ Graceful restart with state persistence</li>
              <li>â€¢ Version negotiation</li>
              <li>â€¢ Agent-based economic simulation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Track B: Operational -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-accent-blue/20">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-blue mb-3">Track B: Operational Hardening âœ…</h3>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-4">
            Production-grade operations and economic validation.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-1 text-sm">
            <li>â€¢ B1: Operational hardening (backup, monitoring, graceful restart)</li>
            <li>â€¢ B3: Economic modeling (agent-based simulation, stability analysis)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Pilot Web UI -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-accent-purple/20">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-purple mb-3">Pilot Web UI âœ…</h3>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-4">
            Production-ready dashboard for cooperative communities.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-1 text-sm">
              <li>â€¢ Dashboard with balance tracking</li>
              <li>â€¢ Activity charts and history</li>
              <li>â€¢ Time/credit logging interface</li>
              <li>â€¢ Member directory with search</li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-1 text-sm">
              <li>â€¢ Governance and voting UI</li>
              <li>â€¢ Full mobile support</li>
              <li>â€¢ CSV export for treasurers</li>
              <li>â€¢ Docker deployment ready</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Next: Track C1 -->
        <div class="bg-accent-glow/10 p-6 rounded-lg border border-accent-glow/30">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-glow mb-3">Next: Track C1 - Pilot Deployment ðŸš€</h3>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-4">
            Select and deploy with actual cooperative communities. This is the next milestone.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-1 text-sm">
            <li>â€¢ Community selection and onboarding</li>
            <li>â€¢ Real-world timebank pilots</li>
            <li>â€¢ Mutual credit system deployment</li>
            <li>â€¢ Feedback integration and iteration</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Deploy</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-light-slate mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          ICN is a substrate daemon for the cooperative internet. 20 phases complete,
          1,134+ tests passing, ready for cooperative community pilots.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/get-started" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-accent-primary text-midnight-navy font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-primary/90 transition-all">
            Get Started
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-transparent border-2 border-accent-primary text-accent-primary font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-primary hover:text-midnight-navy transition-all">
            View Source Code
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
